              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kd4071_step3",
                "text": "To pair the wall switch with the Vera:<br/>1 / Simultaneously press button 1 and 2 of your switch for one second as shown in the following diagram. The light in the switch will blink red.<br/>2 / Then press button 1 within 10 seconds. The LED will blink red / green to validate the procedure.<br/>Several attempts are sometimes necessary.<br/><b>As soon as this device will be associated with your Vera, you will be automatically redirected to the last step of the installation.</b><br/><br/><b>Tip</b>: To recognize the top and bottom of the switch, simultaneously press and quickly on the ends of two buttons. The light that appear to be positioned at the top."
